## Testing Strong Parameters

```ruby
test "filters unpermitted parameters" do
  sign_in_as @user
  
  post articles_url, params: {
    article: {
      title: "Test",
      body: "Body",
      admin_only_field: "hacked"
    }
  }
  
  article = Article.last
  assert_nil article.admin_only_field
end
```

